data.title: Nicholas Tse, Cecilia Cheung marry
data.meta_description: Hong Kong actors Nicholas Tse (L) and Cecilia Cheung pose before their radio program in Hong Kong in this September 21, 2001 file photo. Cheung's manager confirmed that Cheung and Tse married on an unspecified date, local media reported on Saturday. [Reuters]
data.text:
Hong Kong actors Nicholas Tse (L) and Cecilia Cheung pose before their radio program in Hong Kong in this September 21, 2001 file photo. Cheung's manager confirmed that Cheung and Tse married on an unspecified date, local media reported on Saturday. [Reuters]
